      "value": "<p><strong>Element&nbsp;</strong>fire;&nbsp;<strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>utility (Sp);&nbsp;<strong>Level&nbsp;</strong>3;&nbsp;<strong>Burn&nbsp;</strong>0<br><strong>Saving Throw&nbsp;</strong>Fortitude negates; see text;&nbsp;<strong>SR&nbsp;</strong>no</p>\n<p>You transform a source of open flame within 120 feet into a cloud of choking smoke, filling a 20-foot-radius spread and affecting vision like a smokestick. All creatures that begin their turns inside the area become sickened as long as they remain in the smoke and for 1d4+1 rounds thereafter (Fortitude negates).</p>",
